{"tha-ap543:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap543:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap543:0.3":"1 Lakundabhaddiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap543:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap543:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap543:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap543:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap543:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap543:2.2":"setthiputto mahaddhano; ","tha-ap543:2.3":"Janghaviharam vicaram, ","tha-ap543:2.4":"sangharamam agacchaham. ","tha-ap543:3.1":"Tada so lokapajjoto, ","tha-ap543:3.2":"dhammam desesi nayako; ","tha-ap543:3.3":"Manjussaranam pavaram, ","tha-ap543:3.4":"savakam abhikittayi. ","tha-ap543:4.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","tha-ap543:4.2":"karam katva mahesino; ","tha-ap543:4.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap543:4.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","tha-ap543:5.1":"Tada buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap543:5.2":"sanghamajjhe vinayako; ","tha-ap543:5.3":"‘Anagatamhi addhane, ","tha-ap543:5.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","tha-ap543:6.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap543:6.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap543:6.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap543:6.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap543:7.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap543:7.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap543:7.3":"Bhaddiyo nama namena, ","tha-ap543:7.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap543:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap543:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap543:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap543:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap543:9.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap543:9.2":"phusso uppajji nayako; ","tha-ap543:9.3":"Durasado duppasaho, ","tha-ap543:9.4":"sabbalokuttamo jino. ","tha-ap543:10.1":"Caranena ca sampanno, ","tha-ap543:10.2":"braha uju patapava; ","tha-ap543:10.3":"Hitesi sabbasattanam, ","tha-ap543:10.4":"bahum mocesi bandhana. ","tha-ap543:11.1":"Nandaramavane tassa, ","tha-ap543:11.2":"ahosim phussakokilo; ","tha-ap543:11.3":"Gandhakutisamasanne, ","tha-ap543:11.4":"ambarukkhe vasamaham. ","tha-ap543:12.1":"Tada pindaya gacchantam, ","tha-ap543:12.2":"dakkhineyyam jinuttamam; ","tha-ap543:12.3":"Disva cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap543:12.4":"manjunabhinikujaham. ","tha-ap543:13.1":"Rajuyyanam tada gantva, ","tha-ap543:13.2":"supakkam kanakattacam; ","tha-ap543:13.3":"Ambapindam gahetvana, ","tha-ap543:13.4":"sambuddhassopanamayim. ","tha-ap543:14.1":"Tada me cittamannaya, ","tha-ap543:14.2":"mahakaruniko jino; ","tha-ap543:14.3":"Upatthakassa hatthato, ","tha-ap543:14.4":"pattam pagganhi nayako. ","tha-ap543:15.1":"Adasim hatthacittoham, ","tha-ap543:15.2":"ambapindam mahamune; ","tha-ap543:15.3":"Patte pakkhippa pakkhehi, ","tha-ap543:15.4":"panjalim katvana manjuna. ","tha-ap543:16.1":"Sarena rajaniyena, ","tha-ap543:16.2":"savaniyena vagguna; ","tha-ap543:16.3":"Vassanto buddhapujattham, ","tha-ap543:16.4":"nilam gantva nipajjaham. ","tha-ap543:17.1":"Tada muditacittam mam, ","tha-ap543:17.2":"buddhapemagatasayam; ","tha-ap543:17.3":"Sakunagghi upagantva, ","tha-ap543:17.4":"ghatayi dutthamanaso. ","tha-ap543:18.1":"Tato cutoham tusite, ","tha-ap543:18.2":"anubhotva mahasukham; ","tha-ap543:18.3":"Manussayonimagacchim, ","tha-ap543:18.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap543:19.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap543:19.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","tha-ap543:19.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap543:19.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","tha-ap543:20.1":"Sasanam jotayitva so, ","tha-ap543:20.2":"abhibhuyya kutitthiye; ","tha-ap543:20.3":"Vinayitvana veneyye, ","tha-ap543:20.4":"nibbuto so sasavako. ","tha-ap543:21.1":"Nibbute tamhi lokagge, ","tha-ap543:21.2":"pasanna janata bahu; ","tha-ap543:21.3":"Pujanatthaya buddhassa, ","tha-ap543:21.4":"thupam kubbanti satthuno. ","tha-ap543:22.1":"‘Sattayojanikam thupam, ","tha-ap543:22.2":"sattaratanabhusitam; ","tha-ap543:22.3":"Karissama mahesissa’, ","tha-ap543:22.4":"iccevam mantayanti te. ","tha-ap543:23.1":"Kikino kasirajassa, ","tha-ap543:23.2":"tada senaya nayako; ","tha-ap543:23.3":"Hutvaham appamanassa, ","tha-ap543:23.4":"pamanam cetiye vadim. ","tha-ap543:24.1":"Tada te mama vakyena, ","tha-ap543:24.2":"cetiyam yojanuggatam; ","tha-ap543:24.3":"Akamsu naravirassa, ","tha-ap543:24.4":"nanaratanabhusitam. ","tha-ap543:25.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap543:25.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap543:25.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap543:25.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap543:26.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap543:26.2":"jato setthikule aham; ","tha-ap543:26.3":"Savatthiyam puravare, ","tha-ap543:26.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","tha-ap543:27.1":"Purappavese sugatam, ","tha-ap543:27.2":"disva vimhitamanaso; ","tha-ap543:27.3":"Pabbajitvana na ciram, ","tha-ap543:27.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap543:28.1":"Cetiyassa pamanam yam, ","tha-ap543:28.2":"akarim tena kammuna; ","tha-ap543:28.3":"Lakundakasariroham, ","tha-ap543:28.4":"jato paribhavaraho. ","tha-ap543:29.1":"Sarena madhurenaham, ","tha-ap543:29.2":"pujitva isisattamam; ","tha-ap543:29.3":"Manjussaranam bhikkhunam, ","tha-ap543:29.4":"aggattamanupapunim. ","tha-ap543:30.1":"Phaladanena buddhassa, ","tha-ap543:30.2":"gunanussaranena ca; ","tha-ap543:30.3":"Samannaphalasampanno, ","tha-ap543:30.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap543:31.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap543:31.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap543:31.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap543:31.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap543:32.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap543:32.2":"buddhasetthassa santike; ","tha-ap543:32.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap543:32.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap543:33.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap543:33.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap543:33.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap543:33.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap543:34.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma lakundabhaddiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap543:35.1":"Lakundabhaddiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}